 2026 -0700\n\n    feat(sampler): add SampleUsageTracker for piece playback [T-022@20260425T183959Zb]\n    \n    Accumulate sample plays (id, transposition, fx preset, trigger row) during\n    piece playback into a JournalEntry ready for append_to_journal.\n    \n    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n my-claw/tools/senseweave/usage_journal.py |  65 ++++++++++-\n tests/test_usage_journal.py               | 183 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-\n 2 files changed, 245 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)\n\ncommit 68a2f6d923ce9a87e2e3fc0b52a7e13b58378d59\nAuthor: Anthony Ainsworth <anthony@cascadiantech.com>\nDate:   Sat Apr 25 21:33:58 2026 -0700\n\n    verify(T-022@20260425T183959Za): PASS WITH NOTES — journal schema and serialization tests verified\n    \n    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n sdp/verification/t-022@20260425t183959za-verify.md | 53 ++++++++++++++++++++++\n 1 file changed, 53 insertions(+)\n\ncommit f33edf8c611f0424b218589e2f28ca565b4b097f\nAuthor: Anthony Ainsworth <anthony@cascadiantech.com>\nDate:   Sat Apr 25 21:31:29 2026 -0700\n\n    fix(sampler): define usage journal schema and write tests [T-022@20260425T183959Za]\n\n my-claw/tools/senseweave/usage_journal.py | 55 +++++++++++++++++\n tests/test_usage_journal.py               | 98 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++\n 2 files changed, 153 insertions(+)"}
